  "description": "A low-angle perspective captures a circular pattern formed by the convergence of wooden planks, resembling a fan or the inside of a round structure. The wood is weathered and displays a natural grain. Surrounding the base of this structure is a dense patch of green vegetation, primarily consisting of clover and grass. The lighting is soft and diffused, creating subtle shadows and highlighting the textures of both the wood and the plants. There is a small, white object partially hidden within the vegetation, possibly a stone or a shell.",
